                "scintillator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were 3.2-mm-thick by 38-mm-diam disks of",
                "Pilots B and F plastic scintillator containing 91.6%",
                "carbon by weight. These disks were the same diameter",
                "as the first scintillator of the counter telescope",
                "and were mounted to its upstream face during the",
                "irradiations. No correction was made for the 1.11% 13C",
                "content of the carbon; that is, the results reported",
                "here technically apply to natural carbon."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The targets were irradiated for 20 to",
                "40 min (one to two half-lives of the 11C) and were",
                "then transported to a counting area where the target",
                "scintillator disk was optically coupled to the face",
                "of a photomultiplier tube. This assembly was then",
                "placed in contact with the face of a NaI(Tl)",
                "scintillator inside a lead shield. The 11C positrons",
                "were self-detected by the plastic scintillator, and",
                "the annihilation quanta were detected in the NaI(Tl)",
                "scintillator which had an electronic window set to",
                "include only the 511-keV photopeak pulses. Each",
                "sample was counted for at least three half-lives with",
                "standard beta-gamma coincidence circuity. The 11C",
                "disintegration rate was calculated from the net beta+,",
                "gamma, and beta+-gamma coincidence rates."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Reproducibility corrections ranged from 2% for 30-MeV",
                "pi+ to 13% for 30-MeV pi-."
              ]
            }
          ],
